{"tid":2236711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專家：中華民國或成「一中」合法代表","createTime":"2020-10-09T16:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T02:35:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9bc69e2186f96c257e2893afbad45c9529637233","tid":2236711,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T16:19:00.000Z","msg":"美中新冷戰情勢加劇，美國也開始對華為等陸企進行制裁，反觀臺美互動密切，美國衛生部長艾薩、美國國務次卿柯拉克相繼訪臺，談到美中臺關係的未來發展，專家認為，美國的「一中政策」將會有結構性改變，就是不認為中共可以代表中國，估計美國會把中國降為領事關係，並幫助中華民國重新加入聯合國，另外，「一中政策」合法代表性也可能變成「中華民國」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.epochtimes.com.tw/n323507/%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6-%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%96%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8.html\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com.tw%2Fn323507%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8.html&h=37c03777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（GREG WOOD/AFP via Getty Images）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com.tw/n323507/專家-中華民國或成一中合法代表.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com.tw%2Fn323507%2F%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6-%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%96%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8.html&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzpMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=acc90a1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com.tw/n323507/專家-中華民國或成一中合法代表.html</a>"},{"pid":"2a5591f0bd9803fccf9890cd09acc1f8cc0f0443","tid":2236711,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />被中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a28ccf74fa7c7081f41184643dcddae9bef1b5","tid":2236711,"uid":140538,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09