dBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T17:17:31.000Z","msg":"美國唔行一中政策 可以有兩中<br />\n美國自己都講變成領事關係<br />\n即係仲有外交 而唔係斷交"},{"pid":"4f7d21b6c4a95d81eda07bc0a83cea22716eba8f","tid":2236711,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T17:37:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f3a8863dcbb845414267dd4a92f974f11cff3b2","tid":2236711,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T17:39:04.000Z","msg":"首先要特朗普連任<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現實係敗登瞓住喺度都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed1c38d1a7115a08e48f105bcf3defe3fd9ee25","tid":2236711,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f19ac94ea51a371b2c84f94333e50a295164be48","tid":2236711,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T16:56:04.000Z","msg":"只承認一個中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T17:47:06.000Z","msg":"激鳩死支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23666a7cd3a5a488ee66a0d029a7d1a3c39f4bd4","tid":2236711,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:37:50.000Z","msg":"台灣人都唔想做中國人<br />\n<br />\n大中華膠都cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a8a1ec784ec85d980be0a5aec0bd498ae319df","tid":2236711,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22f0dbed34bb907b879d4059b6117b481028df33","tid":2236711,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T17:17:20.000Z","msg":"如果中共真係倒台(當然極不可能),現成可以套去管治既架構就係中華民國所以中華民國個殼有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:44:04.000Z","msg":"其實可以，因為中華民國之前都係咁寫<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>民國71年（1982年）12月31日的中華民國最高法院71年台上字第8219號判例：「<span class=\"red\">茲我國大陸領土雖因一時為共匪所竊據，而使國家統治權在實際行使上發生部分之困難，司法權之運作亦因此有其事實上之窒礙，但其仍屬固有之疆域</span>，其上之人民仍屬國家之構成員，自不能以其暫時之淪陷而變更其法律上之地位。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本就係將宜家台灣嗰套搬去全中國就可以，只要將呢條疆域法令復行（不過道德教化起碼要100年先可以將支那人變成今日台灣人個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>民國94年（2005年）行政區域停止適用前，公告之行政區域為：<br />\n<br />\n「全國共劃分為35個省，2,045個縣，直轄市14個，省轄市56個，管理局7個，設治局34個，特別旗4個，盟部14個，旗127個，牧場1個，特別行政區1個，地方2個（西藏、蒙古）。」<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"right\">&mdash;&mdash;&thinsp;中華民國年鑑九十四年版</p></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5a6459526f8a923a2d66a813dd1bb4304276c5e3","tid":2236711,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/algotrading.blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/073032_fb1569c8296e5e96bba0d0953d58a51c.jpg?resize=640%2C360&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Falgotrading.blog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F073032_fb1569c8296e5e96bba0d0953d58a51c.jpg%3Fresize%3D640%252C360%26ssl%3D1&h=b33b618a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"625dffde3d7cd740972f61041402bffed790e5c6","tid":2236711,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd2033cdad1ff593c8f83bdd989b923cddb5058d","tid":2236711,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a5591f0bd9803fccf9890cd09acc1f8cc0f0443","tid":2236711,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />被中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T16:53:24.000Z","msg":"咁人地個國名真係中華民國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你可以叫佢「華國」嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:46:01.000Z","msg":"係都叫『民國』啦"},{"pid":"bfd835bac73d3f28bd8939ccf3741088bf5d9b81","tid":2236711,"uid":226955,"like":0